THE GAME
--------

  'ezaMaze' is a Workbench game where you have to get to the exit
of a maze, in the least amount of moves. In each game you play,
the exit is at a different position... and not necessarily at the
edge of the labyrinth, in fact the exit can be located at the
center of the labyrinth...

  To complicate matters a little more, only a small portion of the
labyrinth, a 7 by 7 tile area, is shown. To help you, an arrow
indicates where the exit is located from your current position.

  A feature of the game is that you can choose the size of the
labyrinth you want to play with, from a 11 by 11 spaces size, up
to a 59 by 59 spaces size.

  Have fun!

